	up freeing.

2010-06-05  Mark Probst  <mark.probst@gmail.com>

	* sgen-gc.c, sgen-los.c: New LOS allocator that allocates large
	segments of memory at once, to reduce the number of mmap/munmap
	calls.

2010-06-05  Mark Probst  <mark.probst@gmail.com>

