	* verify.c: added IL_CODE_CALL_NONFINAL_VIRTUAL to track calls to
	non-final virtual calls using call. 

	* verify.c (do_invoke): fixed some TODOs.

	* verify.c (push_arg): set has_this_store for "ldarga 0".

