2008-01-08  Rodrigo Kumpera  <rkumpera@novell.com>

	* verify.c (do_newobj): do delegate verification.

	* verify.c (verify_delegate_compatibility): perform delegate
	verification.

	* verify.c (verify_ldftn_delegate): perform tests related to
	ldftn delegates.

