2007-09-14  Zoltan Varga  <vargaz@gmail.com>

	* gc.c (ves_icall_System_GCHandle_GetAddrOfPinnedObject): Use a return value of
	-2 to communicate to managed code that the handle is not pinned. Fixes #82848.

