	* class.c (class_compute_field_layout): Fix #74549.

2005-04-08 Gonzalo Paniagua Javier <gonzalo@ximian.com>

	* threadpool.c: select() on windows doesn't allow pipe handles, soooo
	use 2 connected sockets instead.

