	* assembly.c: Change corlib name to mscorlib. Add a temp. hack to
	load corlib.dll if mscorlib.dll is not found.
	* assembly.h: Remove corlib name define.
	* class.c:
	* domain.c:
	* image.c: Change corlib name to mscorlib.
	
